#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first sokoban game was created in 1982 by Hiroyuki Imabayashi at the "
"Japanese company Thinking Rabbit, Inc. <quote>Sokoban</quote> is Japanese "
"for <quote>warehouse keeper</quote>. The idea is that you are a warehouse "
"keeper trying to push crates to their proper locations in a warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Prvo igro sokoban je leta 1982 ustvaril Hiroyuki Imabayashi v japonskem "
"podjetju Thinking Rabbit, Inc. <quote>Sokoban</quote> je v japonščini beseda "
"za <quote>skladiščnik</quote>. Ideja je, da ste skladiščnik, ki poskuša "
"potisniti zaboje na njihova prava mesta v skladišču."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The problem is that you cannot pull the crates or step over them. If you are "
"not careful, some of the crates can get stuck in wrong places and/or block "
"your way."
msgstr ""
"Težava je v tem, da ne morete potegniti zabojev ali stopiti čeznje. Če niste "
"previdni, se lahko nekateri zaboji zataknejo na napačnih mestih in/ali vam "
"zaprejo pot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It can be rather difficult just to solve a level. But if you want to make it "
"even harder, you can try to minimize the number of moves and/or pushes you "
"use to solve the level."
msgstr ""
"Samo rešiti nivo je lahko precej težko. Če pa želite, da je še težje, lahko "
"poskusite čim bolj zmanjšati število potez in/ali potiskov, ki jih "
"uporabljate za reševanje ravni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make the game more fun for small kids (below 10 years or so), some "
"collections with easier levels are also included in &skladnik;. These are "
"marked <emphasis>(easy)</emphasis> in the level collection menu. Of course, "
"these levels can be fun for adults too, for example if you don't want to "
"expose yourself to too much mental strain."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bila igra bolj zabavna za majhne otroke (mlajše od 10 let ali "
"podobno), je v &skladnik; vključenih tudi nekaj zbirk z lažjimi stopnjami. "
"Ti so označeni z <emphasis>(enostavno)</emphasis> v meniju za zbiranje "
"ravni. Seveda so te stopnje lahko zabavne tudi za odrasle, na primer, če se "
"ne želite izpostavljati preveliki duševni obremenitvi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game"
msgstr "Igra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The objective of the game is to push all the red gems to the goal squares, "
"which are marked with green glassy round things on the floor."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je potisniti vse rdeče dragulje do vratnih polj, ki so označena z "
"zelenimi steklenimi okroglimi predmeti na tleh."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the cursor keys or the mouse to move about. If you move onto a gem using "
"the cursor keys or the &MMB;, and there is nothing blocking it on the "
"opposite side, then you will push the gem. It isn't possible to pull the "
"gems, so if you push a gem into a corner it will be stuck there. You cannot "
"step over the gems either, so you can also get trapped in a part of the maze "
"by blocking the way with gems. Also note that it isn't possible to push more "
"than one gem at a time."
msgstr ""
"Za premikanje uporabite smerne tipke ali miško. Če se premaknete na dragulj "
"s smernimi tipkami ali &MMB; in ga na nasprotni strani nič ne ovira, boste "
"potisnili dragulj. Draguljev ni mogoče potegniti, tako da, če dragulj "
"potisnete v kot, se bo tam zataknil. Tudi čez dragulje ne morete stopiti, "
"zato se lahko tudi ujamete v del labirinta, tako da zaprete pot z dragulji. "
"Upoštevajte tudi, da ni mogoče potisniti več kot enega dragulja hkrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you notice that you have moved the gems in such a way that the level is "
"impossible to solve, then you can always use the undo feature to go back to "
"a position where the mistake has not yet been made. You can of course also "
"restart the level from the very beginning."
msgstr ""
"Če opazite, da ste premaknili dragulje tako, da je ravni nemogoče rešiti, "
"lahko vedno uporabite funkcijo razveljavitve, da se vrnete na položaj, kjer "
"napaka še ni bila storjena. Seveda lahko tudi znova začnete raven od samega "
"začetka."

