#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni z zaznamki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Set Bookmark</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Nastavi zaznamek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skladnik; allows you to <action>set bookmarks with a level at a particular "
"state.</action> You might use this to save yourself repeating the same "
"initial steps in a level."
msgstr ""
"&skladnik; vam omogoča, da <action>nastavite zaznamke z ravnijo v določenem "
"stanju.</action> To lahko uporabite, da si prihranite ponavljanje istih "
"začetnih korakov na ravni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can have up to ten bookmarks at a time, and access them via the "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap><replaceable>X</replaceable></"
"keycap></keycombo> shortcut, where <replaceable>X</replaceable> is any digit "
"between 0 and 9."
msgstr ""
"Hkrati imate lahko do deset zaznamkov in do njih dostopate prek bližnjice "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap><replaceable>X</replaceable></"
"keycap></keycombo>, kjer je <replaceable >X</replaceable> je katera koli "
"številka med 0 in 9."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Bookmark</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na zaznamek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump to a state you have previously saved as a bookmark."
msgstr "Skočite v stanje, ki ste ga prej shranili kot zaznamek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skladnik; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&skladnik; ima skupno &kde; Element menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več "
"informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."

